the rest of the money.

78
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,356
We only have ten million.

79
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,829
And the race is
only two days away.

80
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,036
However, with this money...

81
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,714
...we could find
someone and rent a car.

82
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:39,509
No one will let us hire a car
if we don't have enough money.

83
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:44,037
Listen, I have to drive with
his car no matter the cost.

84
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:46,953
I'll never be able to
beat Hiziri without it.

85
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:53,036
I willing to beat that if I
had that car all my problems...

86
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,076
...would just disappear.

87
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:57,879
And my former friend
Tamotsu would be filled with envy.

88
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,755
He thinks he's so smart.

89
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:03,832
I just need to prove
that I can do it without him!

90
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:08,118
Answer me! I have a score
to settle with those two,

91
