94
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:21,199
I will not give it to some freak...

95
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:24,158
It's mine, get lost.

96
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:27,359
You will never get my car.

97
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:29,635
Even if you got on
your hands and knees.

98
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:32,788
Don't you ever give up?
Listen I will...

99
