someone who could hire a car.

102
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:47,758
I don't think it's possible.
It's too late.

103
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,800
The deadline to
register for the next race...

104
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,871
...will end tomorrow.

105
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,837
