It isn't your fault.

107
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:59,753
- You did everything you could!
- Maybe you're right!

108
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:03,558
Hey, Yasu, do you know
the origins of Gunma?

109
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:06,552
The only thing I know about
Gunma is that he comes from the suburbs.

110
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:10,748
What do you know about his
friend Tamotsu, Hiziri's chief mechanic.

111
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,355
Wasn't it true that the
Gunma and him were best friends.

112
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:17,268
Indeed! They were good friends.
They spent their childhood together.

113
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,470
