117
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,955
Can you spend a few days with me?

118
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:58,553
The gasoline consumption is
expected to decrease with this setup.

119
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:04,029
Listen...

120
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:06,515
I need him to stay alive.

121
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:11,392
Only you can do it!
Prevent him from driving in the race!

122
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:14,278
I could never do that to him.

123
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:17,278
Hiziri trust me and
I cannot betray him.

124
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:20,551
I didn't agree to
work for him out of pity.

125
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,676
But because I wanted to...

126
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,716
help him obtain his best...

127
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,950
performance that he deserves.

128
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:33,073
