I broke my friendship with Gunma.

129
00:08:33,160 --> 00:08:35,116
That can never be undone.

130
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,595
Please, stop it.

131
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:43,276
Don't make me say it again.

132
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:07,436
