I want him to stop.

135
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:17,431
- Your thinking very deeply.
- Salve, Ruiko!

136
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,750
You know, I was
thinking about the next race!

137
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:25,236
