news that will make you happy.

141
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:40,270
The President of the Federation
has given Gunma back his license.

142
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,431
- Are you serious?
- Of course!

143
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:45,473
