phoned asking for you.

144
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:48,836
- She said to call back!
- I'll do that.

145
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:51,272
Bye.

146
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,756
Hiziri!

147
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:04,433
